                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add section to refguide on running G1GC with HBase. There is the intel talk at hbasecon with nice pictures and healthy recommendations, there is our &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=esteban&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;esteban&quot;&gt;Esteban Gutierrez&lt;/a&gt;&apos;s recent experience running G1GC, and the mighty &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=bbeaudreault&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;bbeaudreault&quot;&gt;Bryan Beaudreault&lt;/a&gt; dumped a bunch of helpful advice in the mailing list just now: &lt;a href=&quot;http://search-hadoop.com/m/YGbbupEDoKTrDo/%2522How+to+know+the+root+reason+to+cause+RegionServer+OOM%253F%2522&amp;amp;subj=Re+How+to+know+the+root+reason+to+cause+RegionServer+OOM+&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://search-hadoop.com/m/YGbbupEDoKTrDo/%2522How+to+know+the+root+reason+to+cause+RegionServer+OOM%253F%2522&amp;amp;subj=Re+How+to+know+the+root+reason+to+cause+RegionServer+OOM+&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
